# CODEOWNERS — ai-agent-ui
#
# Maps merge paths to required reviewer groups.
# GitHub enforces these when branch protection rules require CODEOWNER review.
#
# Branching strategy:
#   feature/* → dev → qa → release → main
#
# Syntax: <path-pattern> <@owner-or-team> [<@owner-or-team> ...]

# QA branch: QA team must approve all PRs into qa
/qa/     @qa-team

# Release branch: Tech lead + QA lead must both approve
/release/  @tech-lead @qa-lead

# Main: Senior engineers sign-off (minimum 2 approvals enforced via branch protection)
*        @senior-engineers
